                "title": "雷晶投射"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>，然后分别<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备技能</span>：<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">猜拳三连击 · 剪刀</span>和<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">猜拳三连击 · 布</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/0e809f0cd877c453ef4eb86e7d1b8cbf_7012842692131152315.png",
                "id": "talent8685",
                "key": "猜拳三连击",
                "materials": [],
